categorizing customer's tenure term¶

In [19]:
def tenure_category (x):
    if x <=12:
        return "0-12"
    elif x<=24:
        return "13-24"
    elif x<=36:
        return "25-36"
    elif x<=48:
        return "37-48"
    elif x<=60:
        return "49-60"
    else:
        return "61-72"
    
df_basedata ["tenure_category"] = df_basedata ["tenure"].apply(tenure_category)
